com.prasannjeet.battleship.model

Class PlayerMatches

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.prasannjeet.battleship.model.PlayerMatches

  • public class PlayerMatches
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Prasannjeet Description: Model that persists in MongoDB. Contains the user id's of both players currently playing the game and the primary key, which is the socket id used by both the blayers to communicate with the server. The entry should be deleted after the game finished. Will be updated in next versions. //TODO
